summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 64W, Page 155 of the Official Land Use Map, to rezone certain property located on the east side of South Maynard Avenue at South Brandon Street from Duplex Residence High Density (RD 5000) Zone to General Industrial (IG) Zone and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of Union Pacific Employee Credit Union; C.F. No. 291392).
